      <title>特斯拉提振美国科技巨头，亚洲股市上涨：市场结束</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国科技巨头股价上涨后，亚洲股市预计将高开，华尔街投资者将其高风险收益视为股市牛市的重大考验。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 22:58:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>黄金创纪录的上涨可能源于中国的狂热</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/gold-s-record-setting-rally-may-have-its-roots-in-chinese-frenzy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[黄金今年创纪录的涨幅令市场观察人士感到困惑，因为尽管存在本应抑制金价的逆风，但金价仍在飙升。随着本周价格下跌，原因可能在于中国。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/gold-s-record-setting-rally-may-have-its-roots-in-chinese-frenzy</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 22:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印尼盾暴跌可能导致印尼央行在 2025 年之前无法降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/rupiah-slump-may-keep-bank-indonesia-rate-cuts-at-bay-until-2025</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度尼西亚央行可能会将货币宽松政策推迟到今年晚些时候，甚至是 2025 年初，因为它正在等待美联储利率路径的不确定性和中东持续的战斗结束。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/rupiah-slump-may-keep-bank-indonesia-rate-cuts-at-bay-until-2025</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 22:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国的审查引发企业坚持派发股息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/china-s-scrutiny-sparks-corporate-holdouts-to-hand-out-dividends</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国企业越来越多地提高股息支付，这表明监管推动提高股东回报正在取得成果。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/china-s-scrutiny-sparks-corporate-holdouts-to-hand-out-dividends</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 22:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
