    <item>
      <title>为什么南海可能引发战争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-23/why-the-south-china-sea-could-spark-a-war-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国海警船定期向前往南海菲律宾军事哨所的补给船发射强力水柱。三月份的最新事件是八个月内第六次此类袭击。小费迪南德·马科斯就任总统已近两年，为何这些海域的紧张局势不断升级？北京的行为如何增加与华盛顿对抗的可能性？ （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-23/why-the-south-china-sea-could-spark-a-war-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 21:00:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国 PMI 未达标后新兴市场延续反弹至第二天</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/emerging-market-stocks-sustain-recovery-as-mideast-concerns-ease</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于中东紧张局势有缓和的迹象，且美国经济数据疲软，引发人们对美联储可能采取不那么强硬立场的希望，新兴市场股市连续第二个交易日上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/emerging-market-stocks-sustain-recovery-as-mideast-concerns-ease</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 10:47:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特斯拉深夜飙升，科技巨头咆哮：市场结束</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[科技巨头的上涨提振了更广泛的股市，华尔街投资者将这些公司的高风险收益视为股市牛市的重大考验。]]></description>
